Invocation Name: sustainable seafood pal
des: Nearly 90% of the world’s marine fish stocks are now fully exploited, over-exploited or depleted. If current trends continue, by 2050 there will be more plastic than fish in the ocean. Use Sustainable Seafood Pal to learn how to incorporate sustainable seafood choices into your diet.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
